n Đình Chiểu điếu nghĩa dân trận tử quốc ngữ văn - 讀阮廷沼吊義民陣死國語文</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-ZzgazbvW_31Yn18OxsV6nA">Tùng Thiện Vương</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/Gia-th%C3%A2n-song-th%E1%BB%8D-b%C3%A1i-kh%C3%A1nh/poem-f9JHvurgh7cOpFJt-dmhlg">Gia thân song thọ bái khánh - 家親雙壽拜慶</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/author-lfkyiRMg6zwt6_eiwas6Yg">Vũ Phạm Khải</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/T%E1%BA%A1-tr%C3%AC-xu%C3%A2n/poem-6rhfZvRmtlyU1Z-Y69osfw">Tạ trì xuân - 謝池春</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/author-6xOAUbKdWiBr-eAAn9zXQQ">Lục Du</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Thi%C3%AAn-b%E1%BA%A3o-5/poem-GR0642hjb3cKMK6P0Fscyg">Thiên bảo 5 - 天保 5</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/U%C3%B4ng-Nguy%C3%AAn-L%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng/Th%E1%BB%A5c-ch%E1%BB%A7-Ph%C3%B9-Dung-th%C3%A0nh/poem-_JwK02xhaQkYKr9Sp5Snsw">Thục chủ Phù Dung thành - 蜀主芙蓉城</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/U%C3%B4ng-Nguy%C3%AAn-L%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng/author-HbKyCtS3WFreEebdROalkQ">Uông Nguyên Lượng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Cao/T%E1%BB%B1-ph%E1%BA%ADn-ca/poem-5pG21Opvfb66SZjM6ZPeLQ">Tự phận ca - 自分歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Cao/author-C1VQ72lNTKL4OeInJcXgDw">Nguyễn Cao</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
